Hello, where can I find app_id for my organisation?

Hi there! You can find your app_id by accessing your organization's account settings in the NewsBreak Ad Manager. If you need further assistance, feel free to reach out to our support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com.
how is it called and where is it exactly located?

The app_id is typically referred to as the 'Application ID' or 'App Identifier.' You can find it in the account settings section of your NewsBreak Ad Manager. Look for a section labeled 'Account Information' or 'Organization Details,' where IDs and other key information are usually listed.

If you're unable to locate the app_id in your account settings, it might be best to contact our support team for assistance. You can reach them at adsupport@newsbreak.com, and they should be able to guide you through the process or provide the information you need.
